<div>
  <p>
    We provide a single package containing the server and the client tools. For a
    standard server setup, download the package <strong>Server</strong> and
    install it using the package manager. The <strong>Client Tools</strong>
    package only contain the tools, like arangosh, arangodump, but nor the
    server.

    As an alternative there is a <strong>Tar</strong> containing the server and
    client tools which can be install in any location and which does not
    require root rights for installation.
  </p>
  <hr/>
  <p class="ara_package_line">Packages for the <strong>RPM</strong> package manager:</p>
